{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">ZomBay is a zombie shoot'em up game.<br><br>In ZomBay, players will face relentless waves of the undead while defending their base and their own survival in various heart-pounding game modes, each with unique challenges:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Zombay has 3 modes:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">1. BASE ATTTACK MODE: is based around the idea of WW2's battle of Normandy, while using modern elements from past popular shooting games. Hence the name, ZomBay.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">2. SWAM MODE: Survive waves of endless zombies and gain exp to get the best guns! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">3. CLEAR MODE: Clear each level of zombie as quickly as possible to get the best score! </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In ZomBay you'll find yourself defending your base, as well as your player. In Base Attack Mode zombies will charge the barricades and break through while you desperately try to hold them back! In Swam Mode zombies will swarm the player and increase in numbers over time! In Clear Mode zombies will patrol the map and the player will try to clear the level as quickly as possible!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Features: </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">1. Tons of UNIQUE guns, with ADS (Aim down sights) or alternative firing modes!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">2. ZOMBIE HORDES!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">3. Online leaderboards with anti-cheat</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">4. &quot;Roguelike&quot; gameplay loop (No winning, only getting better each time!) </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">5. Tons of GPU instancing and object pooling for optimal game performance!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">6. Unlock guns for free up to level 60!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">7. Skill tree with upgrades to improve player performance! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">8. Updates with new content and bug fixes!</p></li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"OPEN GAME","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2776480/13ee5deec8a0e7fee84beaaf98284556f38be71c.jpg"},{"name":"UNLOCK LEVEL 1","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2776480/3b80fa2df84ad931e6f83997d79a39843429b959.jpg"},{"name":"UNLOCK LEVEL 2","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2776480/3b80fa2df84ad931e6f83997d79a39843429b959.jpg"},{"name":"UNLOCK LEVEL 3","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2776480/3b80fa2df84ad931e6f83997d79a39843429b959.jpg"},{"name":"UNLOCK LEVEL 4","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2776480/3b80fa2df84ad931e6f83997d79a39843429b959.jpg"},{"name":"UNLOCK LEVEL 5","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2776480/3b80fa2df84ad931e6f83997d79a39843429b959.jpg"},{"name":"UNLOCK LEVEL 6","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2776480/3b80fa2df84ad931e6f83997d79a39843429b959.jpg"},{"name":"UNLOCK LEVEL 7","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2776480/3b80fa2df84ad931e6f83997d79a39843429b959.jpg"},{"name":"UNLOCK LEVEL 8","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2776480/3b80fa2df84ad931e6f83997d79a39843429b959.jpg"},{"name":"UNLOCK LEVEL 9","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2776480/3b80fa2df84ad931e6f83997d79a39843429b959.jpg"}],"total":100},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2776480/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1737422524","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2776480/pa